WEBVTT

00:01:28.311 --> 00:01:33.229
Rhinos are airlifted in C130s
to find sanctuary in this wilderness.

00:01:34.065 --> 00:01:35.215
Lion,

00:01:35.239 --> 00:01:36.481
leopard,

00:01:36.505 --> 00:01:37.733
hyena,

00:01:37.757 --> 00:01:38.928
wild dog,

00:01:38.952 --> 00:01:40.225
cheetah,

00:01:40.249 --> 00:01:44.024
ancient baobab trees
that stand like cathedrals

00:01:44.048 --> 00:01:45.535
under the Milky Way.

00:01:45.559 --> 00:01:49.126
Here, I discovered something obvious:

00:01:49.150 --> 00:01:52.248
wilderness is our natural habitat, too.

00:01:52.272 --> 00:01:56.152
We need these last wild places
to reconnect with who we really are.

00:01:58.129 --> 00:01:59.280
We --

00:01:59.304 --> 00:02:00.602
all seven billion of us --